{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0001","text":"在我指尖可以冒出火百合","structure":{"line_index":1,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情中的幻想","對愛情的期待"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["指尖","火百合"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,9,3,9,5,2,3,9,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zoi6","ngo5","zi2","zim1","ho2","ji5","mou6","ceot1","fo2","baak3","hap6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"指尖","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"可以","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"冒出","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"火","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"百合","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"以「冒出火百合」比喻愛情中不切實際的幻想或期待，語氣帶有想像空間。"},"source":{"title":"逆插玫瑰","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Art Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1223","prev_line_id":null,"next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0002","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0002","text":"然後你會雙眼望見綽綽櫻花","structure":{"line_index":2,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情中的幻想","對愛情的期待"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["雙眼","櫻花"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,3,5,2,4,4,4,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jin4","hau6","nei5","soeng1","ngaan5","mong6","gin3","coek3","coek3","jing1","faa1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"然後","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"會","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"雙眼","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"望見","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"綽綽","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"櫻花","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「綽綽櫻花」描繪出浪漫的景象，與前一句的「火百合」呼應，加強幻想的氛圍。"},"source":{"title":"逆插玫瑰","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Art Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1223","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0001","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0003","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0003","text":"原來即使都是你的花言巧語","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情中的欺騙","對愛情的懷疑"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["花言巧語"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,3,9,3,2,5,3,3,0,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyun4","loi4","zik1","si2","dou1","si6","nei5","dik1","faa1","jin4","haau2","jyu5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"原來","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"即使","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"花言巧語","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「花言巧語」直接點出對方言語的虛假，語氣轉為懷疑與失望。"},"source":{"title":"逆插玫瑰","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Art Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1223","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0004","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0004","text":"但我伸出手照樣接下","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情中的妥協","對愛情的執著"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["伸出手","接下"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,3,3,9,4,2,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","ngo5","san1","ceot1","sau2","ziu3","joeng6","zip3","haa6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"伸出手","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"照樣","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"接下","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「但」字轉折，即使知道是花言巧語，仍選擇接受，展現一種無奈的妥協。"},"source":{"title":"逆插玫瑰","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Art Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1223","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0005","text":"是我一生聽過太少好說話","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["情感的匱乏","對愛的渴望"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["太少","好說話"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,3,3,3,4,4,9,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["si6","ngo5","jat1","sang1","ting1","gwo3","taai3","hou2","syut3","waa6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"一生","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"聽過","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"太少","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"好","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"說話","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「太少好說話」表達了過去情感經驗的匱乏，是造成現狀的原因之一。"},"source":{"title":"逆插玫瑰","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Art Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1223","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0006","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0006","text":"還是根本戀愛大到絕望太難","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情的困境","對愛情的絕望"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["絕望","太難"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,3,9,9,4,2,4,2,2,4,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["waan4","si6","gan1","bun2","lyun2","oi3","daai6","dou3","zyut6","mong6","taai3","naan4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"還是","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"根本","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"戀愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"大到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"絕望","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"太難","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「絕望太難」直接抒發了對戀愛這件事的極度負面感受，語氣強烈。"},"source":{"title":"逆插玫瑰","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Art Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1223","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0007","text":"明明想得很硬接到花便心軟","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["情感的矛盾","對愛情的軟化"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["心軟","花"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,9,3,9,2,4,4,3,2,3,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ming4","ming4","soeng2","dak1","han2","ngaang6","zip3","dou3","faa1","bin6","sam1","jyun5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"明明","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"得","pos":"PART"},{"text":"很","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"硬","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"接到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"花便","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"心軟","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「明明想得很硬」與「心軟」形成對比，展現內心的矛盾與情感的軟化。"},"source":{"title":"逆插玫瑰","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Art Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1223","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0008","text":"難道你 能道歉便算嗎","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["對承諾的質疑","對關係的無奈"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["道歉","算"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,0,2,4,2,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["naan4","dou6","nei5","nang4","dou6","hip3","bin6","syun3","maa1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"難道","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"道歉","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"便算","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"嗎","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"問句語氣，質疑對方僅僅道歉是否就能了事，帶有不滿與無奈。"},"source":{"title":"逆插玫瑰","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Art Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1223","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0009","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0009","text":"我像所有天真女孩寧願相信有一束玫瑰","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["天真的期待","對愛情的憧憬"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["天真","女孩","玫瑰"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,9,5,3,3,5,0,0,2,4,5,3,3,0,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","zoeng6","so2","jau5","tin1","zan1","neoi5","haai4","ning4","jyun6","seon3","jau5","jat1","cuk1","mui4","gwai1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"像","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"所有","pos":"DET"},{"text":"天真","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"女孩","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"寧願","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"相信","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一束","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"玫瑰","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"將自己比作「天真女孩」，表達了對愛情中美好事物的嚮往與相信。"},"source":{"title":"逆插玫瑰","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Art Pop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1223","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_MTIyMw_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
